      <title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司因债务问题暂停向摩尔多瓦供应天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/gazprom-to-halt-gas-supply-to-moldova-on-debt-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 将于 1 月 1 日莫斯科时间上午 8 点起停止向摩尔多瓦供应天然气，原因是涉嫌违反合同义务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/gazprom-to-halt-gas-supply-to-moldova-on-debt-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
