      <title>塞内加尔的 Sonko 绕过议会通过 2025 年预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/senegal-s-sonko-bypasses-parliament-to-adopt-2025-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总理奥斯曼·松科（Ousmane Sonko）批准了明年的预算，绕过了议会对 6.4 万亿非洲金融共同体法郎（102 亿美元）一揽子计划的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/senegal-s-sonko-bypasses-parliament-to-adopt-2025-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:07:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行希望分得 Tether 数十亿美元的稳定币利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/banks-want-in-on-tether-s-billions-in-stablecoin-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直到最近，银行还在羡慕地旁观稳定币市场领导者 Tether Holdings 吹嘘其利润达数十亿美元。现在他们也想加入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/banks-want-in-on-tether-s-billions-in-stablecoin-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
