      <title>对冲基金大举入市，银行牛市势不可挡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/bank-bull-run-seen-thundering-onward-with-hedge-funds-loaded-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从任何标准来看，今年都是美国银行股表现亮眼的一年。对于该行业许多最受尊敬的观察家来说，最好的还在后头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/bank-bull-run-seen-thundering-onward-with-hedge-funds-loaded-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
