      <title>意大利 2025 年预算获得议会批准，为 Meloni 带来助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/italy-s-2025-budget-approved-in-boost-for-giorgia-meloni</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在年底最后期限前几天，意大利议会最终批准了 2025 年预算，这是总理乔治亚·梅洛尼的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/italy-s-2025-budget-approved-in-boost-for-giorgia-meloni</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 12:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍尔茨曼告诉《信使报》：欧洲央行可能考虑等待下次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ecb-may-mull-waiting-before-next-rate-cut-holzmann-tells-kurier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员罗伯特·霍尔茨曼表示，如果能源价格引发的通胀风险或欧元进一步贬值，欧洲央行可能考虑等待更长时间再进行下一次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ecb-may-mull-waiting-before-next-rate-cut-holzmann-tells-kurier</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 07:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰-俄罗斯天然气过境协议面临关键时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ukraine-russia-gas-transit-deal-faces-critical-moment-of-truth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰天然气运输的未来正处于转折点。如果周三之前不能达成最后协议，数十亿立方米的天然气运输可能会中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ukraine-russia-gas-transit-deal-faces-critical-moment-of-truth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
